dc_title_s: Nova et integra vniversi orbis descriptio; Orontius F. Delph., ad lectorem; vale 1531, mense Iulio.; Nova et integra universi orbis descriptio
dc_description_s: Double-cordiform map. Executed in photolithograpy and printed on old paper. 1 map; 31 x 44 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
